trans-unit.source: Represents a client script element in a Web Form or user control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en klient skriptet element i webskjema eller bruker kontroller under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The ClientScriptItem class represents a `script` element that is contained in a Web document at design time.
trans-unit.target: ClientScriptItem klassen representerer en `script` som befinner seg i et Web-dokument under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: A custom control designer implementation can use a ClientScriptItem object to add client script elements to a Web Form or user control.
trans-unit.target: En egendefinert kontroll designer implementering kan bruke en ClientScriptItem-objektet til å legge til klienten skriptelementer i en webskjema eller bruker.

trans-unit.source: At design time, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner> class to set or examine client script elements that are contained in a document, such as a Web form, a Web server control, a content page, or a master page, on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Under utformingen, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>klassen for å angi eller undersøke klienten skriptelementer som finnes i et dokument, for eksempel et webskjema, server formålet, innhold-siden eller hoveddokumentet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Retrieve the collection of client script elements that are contained within the Web document by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hente samlingen av klienten skriptelementer som finnes i Web-dokumentet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: Add a client script element to the Web document by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Legg til en klient skriptet elementet Web-dokumentet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a `script` element either contains script statements or specifies an external location for script statements.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis en `script` elementet inneholder skriptsetninger eller angir en ekstern plassering for skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: The `script` element can optionally define the language of the script statements.
trans-unit.target: Den `script` elementet kan eventuelt angi språket for skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A> constructor to initialize the properties for a new script object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren initialisere egenskaper for en ny skriptobjektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the ClientScriptItem properties to examine the `script` object attributes and contents.
trans-unit.target: Bruk egenskapene ClientScriptItem til å undersøke den `script` objekt attributter for og innholdet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Language%2A> property represents the `language` attribute of the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Language%2A>egenskapen representerer den `language` for den `script` element.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Language%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A> property represents the `src` attribute.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>egenskapen representerer den `src` attributtet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A> property represents the script statements to be executed on the client that are contained in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A>egenskapen representerer skriptsetninger som skal kjøres på klienten som finnes i den `script` element.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the ClientScriptItem class to manage scripts that are to be executed at design-time.
trans-unit.target: Bruk klassen ClientScriptItem for å administrere skript som skal utføres under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: To manage client script elements at run time, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil administrere klienten skriptelementer ved kjøretid, kan du bruke <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: For more information about using client scripts at run time, see [Client Script in ASP.NET Web Pages](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker klientskript ved kjøretid, se [klienten skriptet i ASP.NET Web Pages](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The ClientScriptItem class represents `script` elements at design time that are ultimately parsed and run in the client browser.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For ClientScriptItem representerer `script` elementer på utformingstidspunktet til slutt analysere og kjøres i klientleseren.

trans-unit.source: Because the `script` elements that are generated for the ClientScriptItem objects are not run on the server, the elements do not contain the `runat="server"` attribute.
trans-unit.target: Fordi den `script` elementer som genereres for ClientScriptItem-objekter ikke er kjøres på serveren, elementene inneholder ikke den `runat="server"` attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem"></xref> class using the provided parameters.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem"> </xref> klasse med de angitte parameterne.

trans-unit.source: Initialize the statements for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem> object by using either the `text` or `source` parameter (not both).
trans-unit.target: Initialisere uttrykk for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem>objektet ved hjelp av enten den `text` eller `source` parameteren (ikke begge).</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem>

trans-unit.source: Use `text` to initialize the script using an input string that contains the statements.
trans-unit.target: Bruk `text` initialisere skriptet ved hjelp av en inndata strengen som inneholder setningene.

trans-unit.source: Alternately, use `source` to initialize a script using a path that contains the script statements.
trans-unit.target: Bruk alternativt `source` å initialisere en skriptet ved hjelp av en bane som inneholder skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: You can specify any of the input parameters as `null` or an empty string (""); the corresponding property is set using the input value, and the `script` element is generated without that property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi inndataparameterne som `null` eller en tom streng (""); den tilsvarende egenskapen angis ved hjelp av inndataverdien, og `script` elementet genereres uten denne egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Using `null` or an empty string ("") generates the following results: - For `text`, the corresponding `script` element does not contain script statements.
trans-unit.target: Ved hjelp av `null` eller en tom streng ("") genererer følgende resultat: – For `text`, den tilsvarende `script` elementet ikke inneholder skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: - For `source`, the `src` attribute is not set in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: -For `source`, `src` attributtet er ikke angitt i den `script` elementet.

trans-unit.source: - For `language`, the `language` attribute is not set in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: -For `language`, `language` attributtet er ikke angitt i den `script` elementet.

trans-unit.source: When a client script block does not specify the script language, the client browser determines the language.
trans-unit.target: Når en klient skriptblokk ikke angir skriptspråket, bestemmer klientleseren språket.

trans-unit.source: - For `type`, the `type` attribute is not set in the script element.
trans-unit.target: -For `type`, `type` attributtet ikke er angitt i elementet skript.

trans-unit.source: When a client script block does not specify the script type, the client browser determines the type.
trans-unit.target: Når en klient skriptblokk ikke angir Skripttype, bestemmer klientleseren.

trans-unit.source: - For `id`, the design host (for example, [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]) will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException>.
trans-unit.target: -For `id`, utformingen verten (for eksempel [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]) vil throw <xref:System.ArgumentNullException>.</xref:System.ArgumentNullException>

trans-unit.source: The contents for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element; a string of script statements to run on the client.
trans-unit.target: Innholdet for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet; en streng med skriptet uttrykk til å kjøre på klienten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""></xref> attribute value for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element, specifying an external source location for the client script contents.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet ved å angi en ekstern kildeplassering for klienten skriptets innhold.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""></xref> attribute value for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element, specifying the language of the script statements.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet angir språket for skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: The type attribute value for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element, indicating the MIME type for the associated scripting engine.
trans-unit.target: Attributtverdien typen for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> element, som angir MIME-type for den tilknyttede skriptmotoren.

trans-unit.source: The ID for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: IDen for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: This argument is required by the design host (for example, [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: Dette argumentet kreves av utformingen verten (for eksempel [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]).

trans-unit.source: id is null (thrown by the design host).
trans-unit.target: ider null (et ved utformingen verten).

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ID" name="ID" href=""></xref> attribute value for the client script element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ID" name="ID" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for klienten skriptet elementet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_ID" name="ID" href=""></xref> value of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ID" name="ID" href=""> </xref> verdien for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""></xref> attribute value for the client script element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for klienten skriptet elementet.

trans-unit.source: The Language property represents the language in which the script statements are written.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen språket representerer språket som er skrevet skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: If the Language property is `null` or an empty string (""), the `language` attribute is not set in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen språk er `null` eller en tom streng (""), `language` attributtet er ikke angitt i den `script` elementet.

trans-unit.source: When a client script block does not specify the script language, the client browser determines the language.
trans-unit.target: Når en klient skriptblokk ikke angir skriptspråket, bestemmer klientleseren språket.

trans-unit.source: The Language property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen språk er initialisert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The language name specified for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""></xref> attribute in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på språket som er angitt for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_language" name="language" href=""> </xref> attributt i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""></xref> attribute value for the client script element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for klienten skriptet elementet.

trans-unit.source: The Source property specifies an external source location for the client script contents.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Source angir en ekstern kildeplassering for klienten skriptets innhold.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the script statements for a `script` element are specified using either the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A> or Source property.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis skriptsetninger for en `script` elementet angis ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A>eller Source-egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the Source property is `null` or an empty string (""), the `src` attribute is not set in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen Source er `null` eller en tom streng (""), `src` attributtet er ikke angitt i den `script` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The Source property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Source er initialisert av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The path to the source file specified for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""></xref> attribute in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Banen til kildefilen som er angitt for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_src" name="src" href=""> </xref> attributt i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the script statements contained in the client script element.
trans-unit.target: Henter skriptsetninger i elementet klienten skript.

trans-unit.source: The Text property represents the statements that are contained in the `script` element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Text representerer setningene som finnes i den `script` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the script statements for a `script` element are specified using either the Text or <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis skriptsetninger for en `script` elementet er angitt med teksten eller <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the Text property is `null` or an empty string (""), the `script` element does not contain any script statements.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen Text `null` eller en tom streng (""), `script` elementet inneholder ikke noen skriptsetninger.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A> property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>egenskapen initialiseres av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: The script statements contained in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Skriptsetninger i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_type" name="type" href=""></xref> attribute value for the client script element.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref uid="langword_csharp_type" name="type" href=""> </xref> attributtverdien for klienten skriptet elementet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the MIME type associated with the <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på MIME-type som er tilknyttet den <xref uid="langword_csharp_script" name="script" href=""> </xref> elementet.
